articles.title: Israel's minister celebrates destruction as more Gaza aid seekers targeted
articles.description: An Israeli minister is celebrating the destruction in Gaza as more aid seekers are targeted [1].

articles.title: Air India crash report shows confusion between pilots after fuel cutoff
articles.description: A preliminary investigation into the Air India crash indicates that fuel switches were cut off just before the deadly crash, and there was confusion between the pilots [1, 5].

articles.title: Trump announces 30% tariffs on EU and Mexico after weeks of negotiations falter
articles.description: President Trump has announced he's levying tariffs of 30% against the European Union and Mexico [3, 5].
